-- EXPRS: application forms

=== simple application | 80
(f x)

=== multiple args | 80
(f x y z)

=== empty parens | 80
()

=== bracket application | 80
[a b c]

=== curly application | 80
{f x}

=== nested application | 80
(f (g x) y)

=== empty brackets | 80
[]

=== empty curlies | 80
{}

=== nested parens | 80
((a))

=== mixed brackets | 80
(a, [b], {c})
---
(a , [b] , {c})
